1
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:08,509
Press down hard on the gas

2
00:00:08,592 --> 00:00:12,263
That's right, there's no compromise

3
00:00:12,346 --> 00:00:16,767
We'll slip through the night

4
00:00:16,851 --> 00:00:19,603
At the final moment push hard

5
00:00:19,687 --> 00:00:23,399
That's right, all the way to zero,

6
00:00:23,482 --> 00:00:27,486
Until we wipe away the days

7
00:00:28,946 --> 00:00:33,367
Gently open your heart

8
00:00:34,410 --> 00:00:37,455
If you pull it close to you

9
00:00:39,915 --> 00:00:41,709
It will reach you, without a doubt

10
00:00:42,626 --> 00:00:44,128
It will come, closer

11
00:00:44,211 --> 00:00:47,006
Now

12
00:00:55,055 --> 00:01:00,394
We're speeding through life,
squeezing it for all of its worth

13
00:01:00,478 --> 00:01:01,729
Our feet are tied

14
00:01:01,812 --> 00:01:05,775
But we still keep going farther

15
00:01:05,858 --> 00:01:11,447
Even if I take it back, and grasp it

16
00:01:11,530 --> 00:01:13,908
If you're not the one
There will be no meaning

17
00:01:13,991 --> 00:01:20,247
And so we'll go far off into the distance.

18
00:01:36,180 --> 00:01:39,058
Ugh...what are you here for now?

19
00:01:39,141 --> 00:01:43,729
It's our reunion after so long,
and you're awfully cold.

20
00:01:44,772 --> 00:01:48,192
Don't tell me that you came to
assassinate Lord Hokage?

21
00:01:48,275 --> 00:01:50,319
No, no...

22
00:01:50,402 --> 00:01:53,280
I don't have enough
subordinates for that yet...

23
00:01:53,364 --> 00:01:55,825
I've heard of the excellence ones
of this village

24
00:01:55,908 --> 00:01:57,451
and thought I'd put dibs on them.

25
00:02:02,832 --> 00:02:07,419
A little while ago, I gave that
same Curse Mark as a present.

26
00:02:09,547 --> 00:02:11,048
There's a kid that I want.

27
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:14,134
Selfish as always.

28
00:02:14,677 --> 00:02:16,178
That kid will die.

29
00:02:17,179 --> 00:02:18,264
Certainly...

30
00:02:18,347 --> 00:02:21,225
The odds are 1 in 10
that he'll survive,

31
00:02:21,308 --> 00:02:25,062
but he may survive just like you did.

32
00:02:26,146 --> 00:02:28,816
This kid, you really like him, huh?

33
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:31,610
Are you jealous?

34
00:02:32,236 --> 00:02:38,784
Are you still holding a grudge that
I used you and threw you away?

35
00:02:40,619 --> 00:02:44,331
Unlike you, that kid will excel...

36
00:02:44,415 --> 00:02:48,294
For one thing, he inherited
the Uchiha ability.

37
00:02:49,837 --> 00:02:52,047
He has beautiful features

38
00:02:52,131 --> 00:02:55,259
and is a vessel who
can become my heir.

39
00:02:55,342 --> 00:02:59,430
If that kid lived,
it makes things interesting.

40
00:02:59,513 --> 00:03:02,641
Be sure not to cancel this test.

41
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:09,023
Three from my village are also
under your care...

42
00:03:09,106 --> 00:03:10,983
Make me enjoy it.

43
00:03:13,694 --> 00:03:17,448
If something happens
to deprive me of my fun,

44
00:03:18,365 --> 00:03:21,535
consider it the end of Leaf Village.

45
00:03:39,887 --> 00:03:42,765
We've secured food and water
after spending half a day.

46
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:46,352
And now most teams have halted activity.

47
00:03:47,978 --> 00:03:50,272
As we planned,
this is the time that we attack.

48
00:03:50,940 --> 00:03:53,525
We'll split up into three
and go scouting.

49
00:03:53,609 --> 00:03:57,196
However, whether we find
other teams or not,

50
00:03:57,279 --> 00:03:59,156
we return to this place.

51
00:04:00,741 --> 00:04:02,326
Got it?

52
00:04:02,409 --> 00:04:04,620
Okay.
Roger.

53
00:04:05,204 --> 00:04:06,956
Okay. Scatter!

54
00:04:14,171 --> 00:04:18,300
Bushy-Brow's Pledge:
Undying Love and Protection!

55
00:05:12,146 --> 00:05:13,981
