58
00:05:32,249 --> 00:05:33,500
Naruto!

59
00:05:35,711 --> 00:05:37,129
Sasuke!

60
00:05:37,212 --> 00:05:39,631
Did you take care of us?

61
00:05:39,715 --> 00:05:41,300
Thank you, Sakura!

62
00:05:41,383 --> 00:05:43,218
We're totally better because of you!

63
00:05:45,971 --> 00:05:47,181
That's good...

64
00:05:51,769 --> 00:05:58,108
A prey must always stay tense
and flee desperately

65
00:05:58,776 --> 00:06:00,903
