It was just a dream...

68
00:06:32,893 --> 00:06:34,228
Is it daybreak already?!

69
00:06:36,355 --> 00:06:37,356
No, no way!

70
00:06:52,746 --> 00:06:53,789
A squirrel?

71
00:06:53,872 --> 00:06:57,000
Don't surprise me like that!

72
00:06:57,084 --> 00:06:58,460
Oh!

73
00:07:02,131 --> 00:07:03,340
That was too close.

74
00:07:04,466 --> 00:07:06,009
Do you think she noticed?

75
00:07:06,093 --> 00:07:08,262
