76
00:07:08,345 --> 00:07:10,806
No, that's not it.

77
00:07:10,889 --> 00:07:14,518
Huh? Then what? What was it?

78
00:07:14,601 --> 00:07:17,187
We'll probably find out if we go closer.

79
00:07:18,355 --> 00:07:21,817
So...we should get going now.

80
00:07:40,919 --> 00:07:45,215
If I can catch all twenty of these leaves
before they hit the ground

81
00:07:45,299 --> 00:07:48,343
