82
00:07:48,427 --> 00:07:51,597
If...if I can't catch
even one of the leaves...!

83
00:07:52,222 --> 00:07:55,350
It'll be an unanswered love forever.
Or rather...

84
00:07:55,434 --> 00:07:57,394
You're too Bushy!

85
00:07:57,477 --> 00:07:58,937
That's what she'll say.

86
00:08:01,023 --> 00:08:03,901
One, two, three, four...
five, six, seven, eight...

87
00:08:03,984 --> 00:08:06,195
nine, ten, eleven, twelve, thirteen, fourteen,
fifteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen,

88
00:08:06,278 --> 00:08:11,033
nine...!
Ugh, nineteen...

89
00:08:11,116 --> 00:08:12,492
One more!

90
00:08:15,537 --> 00:08:17,080
That's...!

91
00:08:23,629 --> 00:08:25,631
Phew...just in time.

92
00:08:27,132 --> 00:08:30,802
This is called a Paper Bomb
and it explodes after some time.

93
00:08:31,887 --> 00:08:33,931
Who did such an awful thing?

94
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:44,024
Stop hiding and come out.

95
00:08:44,858 --> 00:08:47,569
Shoot! We scrambled to hide, you know?!

96
00:08:47,653 --> 00:08:51,740
Man, he's a damn pain
and we've been discovered!

97
00:08:51,823 --> 00:08:55,827
Strategy One, "hide and let it pass,"
was a failure!

98
00:08:55,911 --> 00:08:58,664
So now we carry out Strategy Two!

99
00:08:58,747 --> 00:09:01,750
Huh? Are you serious?

100
00:09:01,833 --> 00:09:04,294
What? You have a problem with that?

101
00:09:04,378 --> 00:09:06,630
