and does that mean you want to fight?

112
00:09:50,549 --> 00:09:54,803
N-No...
Of course not.

113
00:09:55,804 --> 00:09:57,347
Then get lost.

114
00:09:57,431 --> 00:10:00,976
Stealing a scroll from cowardly wimps
like you

115
