would only make me
the laughing stock of the village.

116
00:10:03,478 --> 00:10:05,605
Y-Yes!

117
00:10:06,189 --> 00:10:09,443
Huh... Really just like cockroaches.

118
00:10:14,489 --> 00:10:16,575
Just as I thought.

119
00:10:16,658 --> 00:10:21,371
A fellow like that wouldn't take
a scroll away from wimps like us

120
00:10:21,455 --> 00:10:23,582
unless we were to turn on him.

121
00:10:23,665 --> 00:10:27,544
All right! Let's go find some wimps!

122
00:10:28,337 --> 00:10:31,465
Like I've been saying
there's no one wimpier than us...

123
00:10:43,435 --> 00:10:45,562
So a no-sleep lookout?

124
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:49,816
But it's not necessary anymore.

125
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:55,280
Wake Sasuke up.
We want to battle with him.

126
00:10:56,156 --> 00:10:57,491
Y-You bastards...

127
00:11:00,285 --> 00:11:01,912
What're you saying?

128
00:11:01,995 --> 00:11:03,830
What is it you're after?

129
00:11:03,914 --> 00:11:07,042
I know the one called Orochimaru
is calling the shots from the shadows!

130
00:11:07,125 --> 00:11:08,210
Huh?!

131
00:11:08,794 --> 00:11:11,546
What's that strange bruise on
the back of Sasuke's neck?

132
00:11:12,172 --> 00:11:14,049
