133
00:11:14,132 --> 00:11:15,634
How can you say you want to fight him?!

134
00:11:16,593 --> 00:11:21,348
I wonder...what he has on his mind?

135
00:11:22,808 --> 00:11:26,978
However, I can't stay quiet
after hearing that.

136
00:11:27,062 --> 00:11:31,066
I will kill this girl,
I'll also kill this Sasuke character.

137
00:11:35,821 --> 00:11:37,697
Wait, Zaku.

138
00:11:37,781 --> 00:11:39,199
Huh? What is it?

139
00:11:42,702 --> 00:11:44,454
It's so cliché.

140
00:11:45,122 --> 00:11:47,958
It's the color of dirt
that's just been dug up.

141
00:11:48,041 --> 00:11:51,253
This grass, it doesn't grow in
a place like this, does it?

142
00:11:51,336 --> 00:11:52,462
Darn!

143
00:11:53,046 --> 00:11:55,132
You know, with a trap...

144
00:11:55,215 --> 00:11:58,093
there's no point unless you
make it so it's not discovered.

145
00:12:00,637 --> 00:12:02,931
Huh, how ridiculous!

146
00:12:03,014 --> 00:12:06,893
So that Kunai knife was so the squirrel
wouldn't be caught in the trap?

147
00:12:08,103 --> 00:12:09,521
We kill her now!

148
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,443
A log?!

149
00:12:14,526 --> 00:12:17,028
A trap above too? Watch out!

150
00:12:17,904 --> 00:12:19,197
Just kidding.

151
00:12:20,991 --> 00:12:22,451
What?!

152
00:12:22,534 --> 00:12:25,745
Clearly you have no talent.

153
00:12:25,829 --> 00:12:29,875
Someone like you needs to
make more of an effort or else!

154
00:12:31,126 --> 00:12:32,919
Leaf Hurricanes!

155
00:12:38,383 --> 00:12:40,844
What?! This guy...

156
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:44,848
Then you also should...make an effort!

157
00:12:45,891 --> 00:12:46,975
Who are you?

158
00:12:47,058 --> 00:12:51,646
I'm the beautiful blue beast
of Leaf Village, Rock Lee!

159
00:13:04,868 --> 00:13:06,453
Why are you here?

160
00:13:06,536 --> 00:13:07,996
I will always appear...

161
00:13:08,497 --> 00:13:11,750
whenever you're in trouble!

162
00:13:14,669 --> 00:13:15,754
Or should I say...

163
00:13:15,837 --> 00:13:20,008
It was really because of you,
now run along.

164
00:13:26,014 --> 00:13:29,726
But right now, I'm also
your enemy!

165
00:13:30,352 --> 00:13:32,145
I did say this once before, didn't I?

166
00:13:34,439 --> 00:13:36,316
That I'll protect you until I die.

167
00:13:39,778 --> 00:13:41,738
Please go out with me!

168
00:13:41,821 --> 00:13:44,407
I'll protect you until I die!

169
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:47,661
Oh...

170
00:13:47,744 --> 00:13:49,704
T-Thanks.

171
00:13:49,788 --> 00:13:50,997
Yes!

172
00:13:51,081 --> 00:13:54,626
Perfect! I did it!
Gu Sensei, that was perfect!

173
00:13:57,712 --> 00:13:59,631
I guess it can't be helped...

174
00:14:00,173 --> 00:14:03,593
Zaku. I'll give you Sasuke.

175
00:14:04,844 --> 00:14:06,930
I will kill them!

176
00:14:08,098 --> 00:14:11,560
As far as I can tell,
Sakura is in no condition to fight.

177
00:14:12,686 --> 00:14:16,189
That Bushy-Brow guy is
pretty proficient with Taijutsu...

178
00:14:16,273 --> 00:14:18,024
Looks like I can have some fun!

179
00:14:27,409 --> 00:14:31,454
There is a trick to your attack,
isn't there?

180
00:14:31,538 --> 00:14:33,290
I won't just simply avoid it.

181
00:14:34,416 --> 00:14:37,002
You showed me your Jutsu before.

182
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:42,924
This guy...he's strong.

183
00:14:43,008 --> 00:14:44,384
Having said that,

184
00:14:44,467 --> 00:14:46,511
the odds aren't good since
it's one versus three.

185
00:14:46,595 --> 00:14:48,638
