might easily be beaten.

196
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,263
What?!

197
00:15:32,182 --> 00:15:35,143
All right, all right,
I apologize for irritating you.

198
00:15:35,977 --> 00:15:38,521
What a pain...

199
00:15:38,605 --> 00:15:43,652
I say one negative thing about
Sasuke and I get the evil eye, every time...

200
00:15:44,319 --> 00:15:47,155
There's no way Sasuke
could be taken down!

201
00:15:47,238 --> 00:15:49,824
Sakura's a different matter though!

202
00:15:54,371 --> 00:15:55,830
Huh?!

203
00:15:56,748 --> 00:15:58,833
Hey! Sasuke has collapsed...

204
00:15:58,917 --> 00:16:01,795
Huh?!
...and Sakura is fighting.

205
00:16:01,878 --> 00:16:03,213
What did you say?

206
00:16:08,468 --> 00:16:09,594
Hey!

207
00:16:11,721 --> 00:16:13,556
He's late.

208
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,183
That Lee...

209
00:16:15,934 --> 00:16:17,394
Something's not right.

210
00:16:17,477 --> 00:16:19,979
He's always precise about time.

211
00:16:21,314 --> 00:16:23,233
Perhaps he ran into the enemy...

212
00:16:24,901 --> 00:16:26,403
Could it be...?

213
00:16:26,486 --> 00:16:29,280
Huh, that wouldn't have happened.

214
00:16:30,365 --> 00:16:32,909
In any case, let's find Lee!

215
00:16:32,992 --> 00:16:33,993
Right!

216
00:16:40,875 --> 00:16:43,795
Yes! I've finally mastered it!
Yes! Yes!

217
00:16:44,504 --> 00:16:48,800
My friends, there's no reason
to give up on your youth!

218
00:16:56,808 --> 00:16:57,809
This Jutsu...

219
00:16:57,892 --> 00:17:01,062
In the end, only Lee
could make it his own.

220
00:17:01,146 --> 00:17:02,188
Yahoo!

221
00:17:02,272 --> 00:17:04,524
– Hey Lee...
– I did it! I will do it!

222
00:17:04,607 --> 00:17:06,192
– Lee!
– When I try! I try!

223
00:17:06,276 --> 00:17:07,569
Hey, Lee!

224
00:17:09,654 --> 00:17:11,406
Hey!

225
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:18,705
Listen to this passionate message
from your teacher!

226
00:17:18,788 --> 00:17:20,623
Oh...what is it?!

227
00:17:20,707 --> 00:17:22,667
Please tell me using hip words.

228
00:17:25,712 --> 00:17:28,089
This Jutsu, the "Lotus"...

229
00:17:28,173 --> 00:17:30,258
it will be dealt with henceforth
as a forbidden Jutsu.

230
00:17:30,341 --> 00:17:32,051
– What?!
– Huh?!

231
00:17:33,678 --> 00:17:35,013
W-What do you mean?

232
00:17:35,847 --> 00:17:40,393
This Jutsu poses a great burden
on the cells of the muscles,

233
00:17:40,477 --> 00:17:42,520
it's a kind of "Self-sacrificing Technique."

234
00:17:43,688 --> 00:17:47,734
Humans normally utilize,
at most, 20 percent...

235
00:17:47,817 --> 00:17:50,278
of the "power" that the muscles have.

236
00:17:50,361 --> 00:17:52,822
Do you understand?
Only 20 percent!

237
00:17:52,906 --> 00:17:55,742
And if nearly 100 percent
of the "power" is used

238
00:17:55,825 --> 00:17:57,994
the muscles themselves will disintegrate.

239
00:17:58,077 --> 00:18:02,665
So, the brain usually controls the "power."

240
00:18:03,249 --> 00:18:08,713
However, this Jutsu forces the
brain's limiter to go off by using Chakra,

241
00:18:08,797 --> 00:18:12,425
allowing high speed continuous Taijutsu...

242
00:18:12,509 --> 00:18:16,137
In other words, this is a dangerous Jutsu
which relies on a secret technique

243
00:18:16,221 --> 00:18:19,849
that brings forth "power" almost
to the limit of one's body.

244
00:18:21,768 --> 00:18:24,437
So the only time it is all right
to use this Jutsu

245
00:18:24,521 --> 00:18:26,481
is when a certain condition is met...

246
00:18:27,524 --> 00:18:29,984
So...when is that?

247
00:18:31,903 --> 00:18:32,946
Are you ready?

248
00:18:33,029 --> 00:18:34,823
Take this to heart...

249
00:18:35,740 --> 00:18:37,951
The condition is...

250
00:18:41,162 --> 00:18:42,831
The condition is...

251
00:18:47,544 --> 00:18:49,212
Guy Sensei...

252
00:18:49,295 --> 00:18:52,549
I will utilize that Jutsu without reserve.

253
00:18:53,716 --> 00:18:55,802
Because this is the time you said..

254
00:18:59,848 --> 00:19:02,100
"When protecting a precious person!"

255
00:19:04,143 --> 00:19:05,228
He disappeared?!

256
00:19:10,024 --> 00:19:11,609
It's just the beginning.

257
00:19:19,117 --> 00:19:20,493
Oh, oh no!

258
00:19:20,577 --> 00:19:22,996
There's no way he can break his fall!

259
00:19:23,079 --> 00:19:25,290
Take this!

260
00:19:25,373 --> 00:19:27,041
Primary Lotus!

261
00:19:35,383 --> 00:19:36,509
This feeling...

262
00:19:38,928 --> 00:19:40,179
Well well...

263
00:19:43,182 --> 00:19:44,851
Just in time.

264
00:19:53,818 --> 00:19:55,194
T-That's impossible!

265
00:19:55,987 --> 00:19:58,448
That is a frightening Jutsu...

266
00:19:58,531 --> 00:20:02,076
It did this much even though
I fell on the spongy dirt.

267
00:20:06,456 --> 00:20:08,917
It's now my turn.

268
00:20:09,834 --> 00:20:12,295
Oh no! With what I just did...

269
00:20:12,378 --> 00:20:13,338
my body still isn't...

270
00:20:17,926 --> 00:20:19,510
Lee!

271
00:20:25,308 --> 00:20:28,436
Your Jutsu is indeed fast.

272
00:20:30,146 --> 00:20:34,776
But our Jutsu exceeds that
and is the speed of sound!

273
00:20:39,447 --> 00:20:43,451
I'll show you there are walls

274
00:20:43,534 --> 00:20:46,120
which effort alone can
never break through.

275
00:21:05,390 --> 00:21:10,019
Hey, can you hear it?

276
00:21:10,103 --> 00:21:16,985
The clear, blue sky goes on and on

277
00:21:19,237 --> 00:21:26,244
The ocean spans limitlessly

278
00:21:28,371 --> 00:21:35,253
Please keep that smile on your face forever

279
00:21:37,505 --> 00:21:43,011
Or else I'll cry

280
00:21:43,094 --> 00:21:46,848
You won't have to search around you

281
00:21:46,931 --> 00:21:50,935
It's all ok now.

282
00:21:51,019 --> 00:21:55,982
Everyone is inside

283
00:21:56,065 --> 00:21:59,736
this hand

284
00:21:59,819 --> 00:22:04,866
when you want to cry, and you want to run away

285
00:22:04,949 --> 00:22:09,454
When you forget what happiness is

286
00:22:09,537 --> 00:22:13,416
Just sing.

287
00:22:13,499 --> 00:22:18,629
Light is born, and darkness was born

288
00:22:18,713 --> 00:22:20,882
The two are one

289
00:22:20,965 --> 00:22:27,263
Harmonia, feel the telepathy

290
00:22:27,805 --> 00:22:32,852
Hey, can you hear it?

291
00:22:36,647 --> 00:22:39,901
I'm so frustrated!
I'm just pulling feet again.

292
00:22:40,777 --> 00:22:44,697
I'm always just being protected.
I always just watch them from behind.

293
00:22:44,781 --> 00:22:48,159
This time, I need to protect everyone!

294
00:22:48,242 --> 00:22:50,620
Naruto, Sakuke, Lee!

295
00:22:50,703 --> 00:22:54,082
I want to be like you too!

296
00:22:54,665 --> 00:22:58,294
Next episode:
"Sakura Blossoms!"

297
00:22:58,377 --> 00:23:01,214
Please watch my battle...

298
